<h1><u>Create a new Npc</u></h1>

<form action= "/npcs" method = "POST">

<h3><u>Basic Information:</u></h3>
<p>Name: <input type = "text" name="npcs[name]"></p>
<p>Challenge Rating: <input type = "text" name="npcs[cr_rating]"></p>
<p>Level:<input type = "text" name="npcs[level]"></p>
<p>Experience points for encounter: <input type = "text" name="npcs[exp]"></p>
<p>Species: <input type = "text" name="npcs[species]"></p>
<p>Class: <input type = "text" name="npcs[npc_class]"></p>

<h3><u>Defensive Stats:</u></h3>
<p>Hit Points: <input type = "text" name="npcs[hp]"></p>
<p>Resolve Points: <input type = "text" name="npcs[rp]"></p>
<p>Energy Armor Class: <input type = "text" name="npcs[eac]"></p>
<p>Kinetic Armor Class: <input type = "text" name="npcs[kac]"></p>
<p>Defensive Ability: <input type = "text" name="npcs[defense_ability]"></p>
<p>Immunities: <input type = "text" name="npcs[immunities]"></p>

<h3><u>Saving Throws:</u></h3>
<p>Fortitude: <input type = "text" name="npcs[fort_save]"></p>
<p>Reflex: <input type = "text" name="npcs[ref_save]"></p>
<p>Will: <input type = "text" name="npcs[will_save]"></p>

<h3><u>Offensive Stats:</u></h3>
<p>Speed: <input type = "text" name="npcs[speed]"></p>
<p>Melee Attacks: <input type = "text" name="npcs[melee]"></p>
<p>Ranged Attacks: <input type = "text" name="npcs[ranged]"></p>
<p>Offensive Ability: <input type = "text" name="npcs[offense_ability]"></p>
  
<h3><u>Ability Score Modifiers</u></h3>
<p>1. <input type = "text" name="npcs[ability_mod1]"></p>
<p>2. <input type = "text" name="npcs[ability_mod2]"></p>
<p>3. <input type = "text" name="npcs[ability_mod3]"></p>


<h3><u>Skills:</u></h3>
<p>Master Skill: <input type = "text" name="npcs[master_skill]"></p>
<p>Good Skill: <input type = "text" name="npcs[good_skill]"></p>
<p>Special Abilities: <input type = "text" name="npcs[special_ability]"></p>


<h3>3<u>Additional Notes/Info:</u></h3>
<p>Gear/Loot: <input type = "text" name="npcs[gear]"</p>
<p>Any additional information: <input type = "text" name="npcs[optional_info]"></p>



<input type= "submit" value="Create!">
</form>
